reviews.text:
This is actually pretty darn good. I've been looking for a good recipe for my little MTL 18350 devices and this definitely scratches the itch for a blue slush. I will definitely be making more of this. Personally, the flavor is a bit too high for me but the balance of flavor is great, I will probably mix at 20% flavor next time since I'm not using as much nicotine as the recipe calls for. Mixed at 50/50 with 24mg nicotine and let it steep over night.&#xD;
&#xD;
Update: adding a drop or 2 per 10ml of WS-23 really makes this juice shine!
